verbose_text: Luciferase reporter gene assay identified defective in cullin neddylation 1 domain containing 1 (DCUN1D1) as a novel target gene of miR-195 and the expression level of DCUN1D1 was identified to be negatively regulated by miR-195 in cervical cancer cells.
